sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant FE as 前端 MessageCenter
    participant API as HTTP /api/message/read
    participant MySQL as MySQL
    participant Redis as Redis

    U->>FE: 点击进入消息中心
    FE->>API: markAsRead(senderId)
    API->>MySQL: SELECT COUNT(*) WHERE receiverId=? AND senderId=? AND isRead=0
    MySQL-->>API: unreadCount = 5
    API->>MySQL: UPDATE SET isRead=1 WHERE receiverId=? AND senderId=? AND isRead=0
    API->>Redis: DECR message:unread:{userId} BY 5
    Redis-->>API: remaining = 0
    API-->>FE: 标记成功
    FE->>FE: fetchUnreadCount() → 红点消失
